name: TEMNAI Launch
description:
You've been selected for an interview at Brex Corp's headquarters- a truly prestigious location!  Here you will get to meet High Lord Bexos face to face. If you nail the interview, your future will be set!

Good luck, and welcome to Brex Corp.

Use the arrow keys to move

Use ENTER to select/continue dialogue

Use SHIFT to run

Use ESC to delete
